OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774033869
OL,3,CWarm and sunny weekend - but a cold
OL,4,Csnap brings snow risk next week
OL,6,FAs promised, the UK has enjoyed a
OL,7,Fglorious week of weather, and it's not
OL,8,Fover yet!
OL,10,FA lovely weekend is on the cards with
OL,11,Fthe days officially longer than the
OL,12,Fnights after Friday's Spring Equinox.
OL,13,FBut make the most of the sunshine
OL,14,Fbecause it all goes downhill next week
OL,15,Fwith wintry hazards back on the cards.
OL,17,FHow's the weekend looking?
OL,19,FLet's start with the good news, it's
OL,20,Fgoing to be lovely!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
