PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774033869
OL,3,CWarm and sunny weekend - but a cold
OL,4,Csnap brings snow risk next week
OL,6,FThe difference between night time and
OL,7,Fdaytime temperatures is called the
OL,8,Fdiurnal temperature range and it's an
OL,9,Finteresting watch point for
OL,10,Fforecasters because it helps to
OL,11,Fanticipate hazards and issue warnings
OL,12,Faccurately.
OL,14,FWho's most likely to see the snow next
OL,15,Fweek?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
