PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774033869
OL,3,CWarm and sunny weekend - but a cold
OL,4,Csnap brings snow risk next week
OL,6,FScotland, Northern Ireland, and
OL,7,Fnorthern England are the areas most at
OL,8,Frisk, especially over higher ground.
OL,9,FBut even further south, brief wintry
OL,10,Fshowers or icy patches aren't
OL,11,Fimpossible if the air turns cold
OL,12,Fenough.
OL,14,FHow unusual would it be to see snow at
OL,15,Fthe end of March?
OL,17,FIt would be very unusual to see
OL,18,Fwidespread, heavy snow across the UK
OL,19,Fbut not terribly unusual for northern,
OL,20,Fhigher ground to see snow showers or
OL,21,Feven lying snow at this time of year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
