PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774033869
OL,3,CWarm and sunny weekend - but a cold
OL,4,Csnap brings snow risk next week
OL,6,FIn fact, the latest we've recorded
OL,7,Fsnow in the UK is in June!
OL,9,FThis was quite a widespread event on
OL,10,FJune 2, 1975, with 16cm of snow
OL,11,Freported at Glenmore lodge in
OL,12,FScotland, and snow showers disrupting
OL,13,Fcricket matches as far south as Essex!
OL,15,FAre there any warnings out yet?
OL,17,FNot yet but it's definitely worth
OL,18,Fkeeping up to date as the colder air
OL,19,Fstarts to move in next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
